    "consultant"
  ],
  "dataOwnership": "Tenant-owned. Project records, time entries, documents, and billing history are exportable to JSON/CSV. Client-facing records exportable separately for onboarding/offboarding.",
  "complianceNotes": "Time-tracking, billing practices, professional-services regulations, and client-confidentiality rules vary by industry. Expressed as bundle configuration rather than core behavior."
